<br />
At the very top you should see &lt;em&gt;After moving or deleting an open item:&lt;/em&gt;, and here you'd want to select the option &lt;strong&gt;Open the previous item&lt;/strong&gt; from the drop-down. Then simply click on &lt;strong&gt;OK&lt;/strong&gt; to save the setting.<br />
